OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FA 25-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after a woman was found
OL,8,Fdead in a home.
OL,10,FKyle Howard, of Tweedale Street,
OL,11,FRochdale, is due to appear at
OL,12,FManchester Magistrates on Wednesday, 3
OL,13,FJune, charged with the murder Keeley
OL,14,FAspinall, who was found dead at a flat
OL,15,Fon the Freehold estate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
