OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780563951
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,7,Fproperty on Tweedale Street on 25 May
OL,8,Ffollowing reports of a concern for
OL,9,Fwelfare. Upon arrival, officers
OL,10,Fdiscovered the body of the 44-year-
OL,11,Fold. She died at the scene.
OL,13,FIn a tribute released through police,
OL,14,Fher family said: "Gone too soon.. we
OL,15,Fcan't believe you are gone. We will
OL,16,Falways love you and miss you, love all
OL,17,Fyour family xx."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
