PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780563951
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after woman
OL,4,Cfound dead
OL,6,FSpeaking on the day of Ms Aspinall's
OL,7,Fdeath, Temporary Detective Chief Supt
OL,8,FJamie Daniels said: "We appreciate
OL,9,Fthis incident is likely to cause some
OL,10,Fdistress amongst the public and local
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"I would like to reassure you that we
OL,14,Fbelieve this to be an isolated
OL,15,Fincident, which does not pose any
OL,16,Ffurther risk to the wider public."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
